      "date": "2012-07-03 23:10:51.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4: (2 inline comments)\n\nCould be some small improvements.  I guess the \"valid\" abuse predates this patch, but it definitely doesn't do anything to improve the robustness of this code to just pass down all flags.",
